  <h2>1. What Are Cookies</h2>
  <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the site remember information about your visit. We use localStorage (similar in function to cookies) as our primary storage mechanism for preferences and session data.</p>

  <h2>2. The Cookies / Local Storage We Use</h2>

  <h3 style="color:#FFE566;font-size:1rem;margin:20px 0 10px;">Essential (cannot be disabled)</h3>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>ww-cookie-consent</td><td>Stores your cookie consent preference</td><td>1 year</td></tr>
      <tr><td>ww-wishes-{year}</td><td>Tracks how many wishes you've pinned this year (max 3)</td><td>End of calendar year</td></tr>
      <tr><td>ww-mycode</td><td>Stores your personal WishCode for the referral system</td><td>1 year</td></tr>
      <tr><td>ww-wishcredits</td><td>Tracks your earned WishCredits balance</td><td>1 year</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 style="color:#FFE566;font-size:1rem;margin:20px 0 10px;">Third-Party (optional, require consent)</h3>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Provider</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Policy</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Stripe</td><td>Secure payment processing. Stripe sets its own cookies to prevent fraud and enable payment sessions.</td><td><a href="https://stripe.com/cookies-policy/legal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stripe.com</a></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Google Fonts</td><td>Loads typefaces from Google's CDN. Google may log IP addresses for delivery purposes.</td><td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">google.com</a></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Firebase/Google</td><td>Platform data storage and real-time updates. No advertising tracking.</td><td><a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">firebase.google.com</a></td></tr>
      <tr><td>ipapi.co</td><td>Anonymous IP-based country detection for displaying your flag on your wish note. No account created, no personal data stored.</td><td><a href="https://ipapi.co/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ipapi.co</a></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>3. What We Don't Use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Advertising or tracking cookies of any kind</li>
    <li>Facebook Pixel or any social media tracking</li>
    <li>Google Analytics or similar analytics platforms (we use anonymised platform-level data only)</li>
    <li>Any cross-site tracking technology</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Managing Your Preferences</h2>
  <p>When you first visit The Wish Wall, a cookie consent banner will appear. You can choose to accept all cookies or essential cookies only. You can change your preference at any time by clearing your browser's local storage or contacting us.</p>
  <p>To clear your preferences in most browsers: Settings → Privacy → Clear browsing data → Cookies and site data.</p>

  <h2>5. More Information</h2>
